(Known Limitations) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(The current prototype does not include OCR, full registration, enterprise SSO, multi-) Tj
T*
(tenant user isolation, or a production-grade database. These limitations are intentional) Tj
T*
(because the project is scoped as a solo-student final year additional project.) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(The current evaluation benchmark module was removed from the user-facing demo to avoid) Tj
T*
(misleading fixed benchmark scores. Instead, the project focuses on live document upload,) Tj
T*
(retrieval, citations, grounded answering, and auditability.) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(Future Enhancements) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(The planned future work includes OCR for scanned PDFs, PostgreSQL persistence, document) Tj
T*
(preview, metadata inspection, admin analytics, query history, improved role-based access) Tj
T*
(control, larger corpus testing, and more advanced retrieval evaluation.) Tj
